name: Fox King’s Smiling Face
description: A woodcutter had seen a dark fox on the night of the moon. He saw the fox kneeling to the moon and praying. He looked at the scene with fascination and did not notice that the fox turned and found him! The fox face was full of golden patterns, grinning at him with a chill in his eyes. The smiling face of the king of fox, those who see it will be driven by the king of fox, become the slaves of the fox!
